  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span style=\"font-family:Jost\">Zhirafa drones have a simple claim to fame: they're cheap, durable, and easy to repair, making them an essential tool of most organizations within the Red Decades.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;scrollbar-width:thin;scrollbar-color:var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track);margin:0.5em 0px;color:rgb(13, 11, 12);font-family:Jost;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(234, 234, 234);text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start\"><span style=\"font-family:Jost\">Air drones are dual-rotor, with a unique profile that makes them unmistakably Zhirafa. Their ability to fly gives the user access to a cheap and (relatively) replaceable method of snooping.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;scrollbar-width:thin;scrollbar-color:var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track);margin:0.5em 0px;color:rgb(13, 11, 12);font-family:Jost;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(234, 234, 234);text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start\"><span style=\"font-family:Jost\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;scrollbar-width:thin;scrollbar-color:var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track);font-weight:550\">Uses the @UUID[Compendium.night-city-gang-and-corp-mook-pack.NCGangsnCorpsMooks.5Jr26oqFSDjPu9jV]{RatSec Mini Air Drone} statblock.</strong></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;scrollbar-width:thin;scrollbar-color:var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track);margin:0.5em 0px;color:rgb(13, 11, 12);font-family:Jost;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(234, 234, 234);text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start\"><span style=\"font-family:Jost\">Includes a slot for mounting any 1-handed weapon which could be mounted in a cyberarm - by default, equipped with either a Dartgun or Very Heavy Pistol. Always equipped with a front-mounted <a class=\"content-link\" draggable=\"true\" data-link data-uuid=\"Compendium.cyberpunk-red-core.core_gear.Item.clCxd7qkp2olsKii\" data-id=\"clCxd7qkp2olsKii\" data-type=\"Item\" data-pack=\"cyberpunk-red-core.core_gear\" data-tooltip=\"Gear Item\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;scrollbar-width:thin;scrollbar-color:var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track);cursor:pointer;--content-link-background:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);background:rgb(221, 221, 221);color:var(--cpr-text-normal);padding:1px 4px;border:1px solid var(--color-border-dark-tertiary);border-radius:2px;white-space:nowrap;word-break:break-all\">Video Camera</a>.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;scrollbar-width:thin;scrollbar-color:var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track);margin:0.5em 0px;color:rgb(13, 11, 12);font-family:Jost;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(234, 234, 234);text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start\"><span style=\"font-family:Jost\">See Controlling Drones in the Associated Homebrew document for more details on how to control the drone, once purchased.</span></p>"
    },
